## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [bhlh010 bhlh089]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Anthers on early flowers fail to produce pollen grains, anthers on later flowers produce a small number of pollen grains. Tapetum does not develop normally. Callose cell wall is thinner.
   - [bhlh010 bhlh089]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Normal vegetative growth and floral organs.
   - [bhlh010 bhlh091]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Aborted pollen occasionally observed.  Anther size and number of pollen grains obviously reduced. Tapetum does not develop normally.
   - [bhlh010 bhlh091]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Normal vegetative growth and floral organs.
